KBR is an equal opportunity employer committed to providing an inclusive and
diverse work environment. We encourage candidates of all abilities to apply.

As a Major Service Provider of the Australian Defence Force, an AGSVA security
clearance will be required and compliance to International Traffic in Arms
Regulations (ITAR). As such, our hiring decisions are based on the key
requirements of each role and candidates are selected based on their unique
strengths and experiences.

